overview: This series brings you unbelievably gorgeous girls doing things beyond most women's imaginations. Featured cover girls Red Fox and Angelika Grays have that vacay mentality. Red is fighting with her controlling boyfriend, which pushes her towards Angelika and her man: an experimental couple with an appetite for seducing attached women. But maybe Red wants to be seduced... Eliza Ibarra, Avery Cristy, Sonya Blaze, and Ashley Lane are all mind-blowingly beautiful and game to get it on.
title: Natural Beauties 17
